{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Интегрируйте карты в свое приложение на основе UIKit или SwiftUI."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Шаг 1. Получите API-ключ для MapsNativeSDK","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-1-%D0%9F%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%83%D1%87%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B5-API-%D0%BA%D0%BB%D1%8E%D1%87-%D0%B4%D0%BB%D1%8F-MapsNativeSDK","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Подробнее о вариантах получения ключа читайте на ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/dev.vk.com\/ru\/vkmaps\/general-information\/api-key","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Шаг 2. Подключите MapsNativeSDK к проекту","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-2-%D0%9F%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BA%D0%BB%D1%8E%D1%87%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B5-MapsNativeSDK-%D0%BA-%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B5%D0%BA%D1%82%D1%83","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"В данный момент MapsNativeSDK распространяется с помощью архива с несколькими "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".xcframework"},{"type":"text","text":"-пакетами."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Откройте свой проект с помощью Xcode.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Выберите необходимый target, в котором будут использоваться возможности SDK."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Во вкладке General добавьте все предоставленные "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".xcframework"},{"type":"text","text":"-файлы в раздел "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Frameworks, Libraries, and Embedded Content"},{"type":"text","text":". На скриншоте ниже показан пример добавленных фреймворков в target."}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"addedFrameworks"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Шаг 3. Используйте MapsNativeSDK","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-3-%D0%98%D1%81%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D1%83%D0%B9%D1%82%D0%B5-MapsNativeSDK","type":"heading"},{"level":3,"text":"Импорт SDK","anchor":"%D0%98%D0%BC%D0%BF%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%82-SDK","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Импортируйте ","type":"text"},{"code":"MapsNativeSDK","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" в файл, в котором вы будете использовать карту.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["import MapsNativeSDK"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":3,"text":"Конфигурация SDK","anchor":"%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%86%D0%B8%D1%8F-SDK","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Сконфигурируйте SDK, используя метод ","type":"text"},{"code":"MapsSDKConfigurator\/setup(baseURL:apiKey:diskCachePath:maxCacheSizeBytes:fileTimeoutSec:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Конфигурация с передачей только API-ключа","MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(apiKey: ##API-ключ##)","","\/\/ Конфигурация с передачей дополнительных параметров","MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(baseURL: ##Базовый URL для загрузки тайлов и предустановленных стиле##,","                          apiKey: ##API-ключ##,","                          diskCachePath: ##Путь для хранения файлов кэша на диске##,","                          maxCacheSizeBytes: ##Максимальный размер файлового кэша в байтах##,","                          fileTimeoutSec: ## Время жизни файлов в кэше ###)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"style":"important","name":"Important","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Если не указать путь к файловому кэшу, то SDK не будет кешировать данные в виде файлов.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"},{"level":3,"text":"Конфигурация карты","anchor":"%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%86%D0%B8%D1%8F-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D1%8B","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Создайте конфигурацию для карты с помощью типа "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapConfiguration","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", указав исходные настройки карты."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Кофигурация для карты с использованием предустановленного стиля","let configuration = MapConfiguration(","    center: ##Стартовые координаты центра карты##,","    zoom: ##Стартовый зум карты##,","    predefinedStyle: .simple",")"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Вместо предустановленных стилей вы можете передать стиль, загруженный с помощью типа ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapStyle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" или строку в формате JSON (подробнее в статье ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Styles","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Создание делегата","anchor":"%D0%A1%D0%BE%D0%B7%D0%B4%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%B3%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B0","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Вам необходимо создать объект-делегат карты, в котором в дальнейшем вы сможете обрабатывать события жизненного цикла карты (подробнее в статье ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Lifecycle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"). При создании делегата подпишитесь на протокол ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapViewDelegate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Определение класса-делегата","class BaseMapViewDelegate: MapViewDelegate {}","","\/\/ ...","","\/\/ Создание делегата","let delegate = BaseMapViewDelegate()"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"В дальнейшем данный объект потребуется передать при создании экземпляра типа ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Не требуется реализовывать методы "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapViewDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":", если их функциональность вам не нужна."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"},{"level":3,"text":"Размещение карт на экране","anchor":"%D0%A0%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%89%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82-%D0%BD%D0%B0-%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B5","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MapsNativeSDK могут быть использованы в приложениях, основанных на UIKit и SwiftUI. Далее рассмотрим каждую из платформ."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"warning","name":"Warning","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Убедитесь, что к этому моменту вы сконфигурировали SDK с помощью вызова ","type":"text"},{"code":"MapsSDKConfigurator.setup","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside"},{"level":4,"text":"Использование в UIKit-проекте","anchor":"%D0%98%D1%81%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%B2-UIKit-%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B5%D0%BA%D1%82%D0%B5","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Для использования карты в UIKit необходимо создать объект "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView"},{"type":"text","text":", передав в него конфигурацию, и разместить созданный объект на экране."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class ViewController: UIViewController {","","    override func viewDidLoad() {","        super.viewDidLoad()","        \/\/ Конфигурирование SDK","        MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(apiKey: \"...\")","        \/\/ Создание конфигурации карты","        let configuration = MapConfiguration(center: Coordinates(lng: 37.6156, lat: 55.7522), zoom: 10, predefinedStyle: .main)","        \/\/ Создание объекта карты","        let mapView = MapView(frame: CGRect(x: 0, y: 0,","                                            width: UIScreen.main.bounds.width,","                                            height: UIScreen.main.bounds.height),","                              configuration: configuration,","                              delegate: self)","        \/\/ Размещение карты на экране","        view.addSubview(mapView)","    }","}","","\/\/ Делегат карты","extension ViewController: MapViewDelegate {}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":4,"text":"Использование в SwiftUI-проекте","anchor":"%D0%98%D1%81%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%B2-SwiftUI-%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B5%D0%BA%D1%82%D0%B5","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Для использования карты в SwiftUI необходимо создать объект ","type":"text"},{"code":"MapView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" и передать его в структуру ","type":"text"},{"code":"Map","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Делегат для MapView","class BaseMapViewDelegate: MapViewDelegate {}","","\/\/ View-модель экрана, где будет использоваться карта","final class ContentViewModel: ObservableObject {","    \/\/ Объект карты","    let mapView: MapView","    \/\/ Объект делегата карты","    private let mapViewDelegate: MapViewDelegate","    ","    init() {","        \/\/ Конфигурирование SDK","        MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(apiKey: \"...\")","        \/\/ Создание конфигурации карты","        let configuration = MapConfiguration(center: Coordinates(lng: 37.6156, lat: 55.7522), zoom: 10, predefinedStyle: .main)","        \/\/ Создание делегата карты","        let delegate = BaseMapViewDelegate()","        mapViewDelegate = delegate","        \/\/ Создание объекта карты","        mapView = MapView(configuration: configuration, delegate: delegate)","    }","}","","\/\/ Экран с картой","struct ContentView: View {","    @StateObject private var viewModel = ContentViewModel()","","    var body: some View {","        Map(view: viewModel.mapView)","            .frame(maxWidth: .infinity, maxHeight: .infinity)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/StartUsing"},"metadata":{"role":"article","title":"Начало работы с MapsNativeSDK","modules":[{"name":"MapsNativeSDK"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/startusing"]}],"kind":"article","references":{"doc://MapsNativeSDK/documentation/MapsNativeSDK/MapStyle":{"abstract":[{"text":"Controller for managing map style: sources, layers, and runtime images\/models.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MapStyle"}],"url":"\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/mapstyle","type":"topic","title":"MapStyle","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MapStyle"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapStyle"},"doc://MapsNativeSDK/documentation/MapsNativeSDK/Lifecycle":{"title":"Отслеживание событий карты","role":"article","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Отслеживайте события, происходящие с картой, и программируйте реакцию на них.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/lifecycle","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Lifecycle","kind":"article"},"addedFrameworks":{"alt":"Added frameworks","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/MapsNativeSDK\/addedFrameworks.png"}],"identifier":"addedFrameworks","type":"image"},"doc://MapsNativeSDK/documentation/MapsNativeSDK":{"abstract":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"MapsNativeSDK","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" - библиотека, позволяющая использовать картографические данные и геосервисы VK в ваших iOS-приложениях."}],"title":"MapsNativeSDK","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk"},"doc://MapsNativeSDK/documentation/MapsNativeSDK/Styles":{"type":"topic","role":"article","title":"Оформление карты","url":"\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/styles","abstract":[{"text":"Изменяйте внешний вид карты, рисуйте геометрические фигуры и размещайте маркеры.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Styles","kind":"article"},"doc://MapsNativeSDK/documentation/MapsNativeSDK/MapView":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MapView","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Main object of the Map","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/mapview","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MapView","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView","title":"MapView"},"doc://MapsNativeSDK/documentation/MapsNativeSDK/MapViewDelegate":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MapViewDelegate"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapViewDelegate","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MapViewDelegate"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Interface, that MapView uses to inform its delegate about events on map","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/mapviewdelegate","title":"MapViewDelegate"},"https://dev.vk.com/ru/vkmaps/general-information/api-key":{"title":"портале","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"портале","type":"text"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/dev.vk.com\/ru\/vk